metadata.Plot: Imagine a near-future dystopian world where you and your partner are left stranded, by your broken down car, in the middle of a deserted Detroit city street. You look around at your hostile and foreign environment and then faced with mastering the art of survival, fear, and love. This is the essence of Disruption.
